[
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, \u201cI was the one the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> to <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">anoint</st> you as <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> his <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"05921 03478\">Israel</st>. <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen</st> to <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">says</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03541\" class=\"\">Here is what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>: \u2018I <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">carefully observed</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">how</st> the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st> <st data-num=\"06213 0834 07760\">opposed</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> along the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> when Israel<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">came up</st> from <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egypt</st>. ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> and <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">strike down</st> the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>. <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">Destroy</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">everything</st> they have. <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">Don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"02550 05921\">spare</st><n id=\"1\" /> them. <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">Put</st> them <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">to death</st>\u2014<st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>, <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">woman</st>, <st data-num=\"05768\" class=\"\">child</st>, <st data-num=\"03243\" class=\"\">infant</st>, <st data-num=\"07794\" class=\"\">ox</st>, <st data-num=\"07716\" class=\"\">sheep</st>, <st data-num=\"01581\" class=\"\">camel</st>, and <st data-num=\"02543\" class=\"\">donkey</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">alike</st>.\u2019\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">assembled</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">mustered</st> them at <st data-num=\"02923\" class=\"\">Telaim</st>. There were <st data-num=\"03967 0505\">200,000</st> <st data-num=\"07273\" class=\"\">foot soldiers</st> and <st data-num=\"06235 0505\">10,000</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. ",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">proceeded</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalek</st>, where he <st data-num=\"0693\" class=\"\">set an ambush</st><n id=\"2\" /> in the <st data-num=\"05158\" class=\"\">wadi</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"07017\" class=\"\">Kenites</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go on</st> and <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">leave</st>! <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">Go down</st> from <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">among</st> the <st data-num=\"06003\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>. <st data-num=\"06435\" class=\"\">Otherwise</st> I will <st data-num=\"05595\" class=\"\">sweep</st> you <st data-num=\"05595\" class=\"\">away</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> them. After all, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">were</st> <st data-num=\"02617\" class=\"\">kind</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01121 03478\">Israelites</st> when they <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">came up</st> from <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egypt</st>.\u201d So the <st data-num=\"07017\" class=\"\">Kenites</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">withdrew</st> from <st data-num=\"08432\" class=\"\">among</st> the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">struck down</st> the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">all the way</st> from <st data-num=\"02341\" class=\"\">Havilah</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">to</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07793\" class=\"\">Shur</st>, <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">which</st> is <st data-num=\"05921 06440\">next to</st> <st data-num=\"04714\" class=\"\">Egypt</st>. ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"08610\" class=\"\">captured</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">Agag</st> of the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st> <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">alive</st>, but he <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">executed</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> Agag\u2019s <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">with</st> the <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st>. ",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "However, <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> and the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"02550 05921\">spared</st> <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">Agag</st>, along <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">with</st> the <st data-num=\"04315\" class=\"\">best</st> of the <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">flock</st>, the <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">cattle</st>, the <st data-num=\"04924\" class=\"\">fatlings</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"03733\" class=\"\">lambs</st>, <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">as well as</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">everything</st> else that was <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">of value</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> They were <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"014\" class=\"\">willing</st> to <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">slaughter</st> them. But they did <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">slaughter</st> <st data-num=\"03605 04399\">everything</st> that was <st data-num=\"0959\" class=\"\">despised</st><n id=\"3\" /> and <st data-num=\"04549\" class=\"\">worthless</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"01961 0559\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>: ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "\u201cI <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">regret</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> I have <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">made</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he has <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">turned away</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">from</st> me and has <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">done</st> what I <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">told</st> him to do.\u201d <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"02734\" class=\"\">became angry</st> and he <st data-num=\"02199\" class=\"\">cried out</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> that <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"07925\" class=\"\">got up early</st> to <st data-num=\"07122\" class=\"\">meet</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> the next <st data-num=\"01242\" class=\"\">morning</st>. But <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> was <st data-num=\"05046 0559\">informed</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> has <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">gone</st> to <st data-num=\"03760\" class=\"\">Carmel</st> <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">where</st><n id=\"1\" /> he is <st data-num=\"05324\" class=\"\">setting up</st> a <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">monument</st> for himself.\u201d Then Samuel <st data-num=\"05437 05674\">left</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">went down</st> to <st data-num=\"01537\" class=\"\">Gilgal</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "When <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to him, \u201cMay the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01288\" class=\"\">bless</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st>! I have <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">fulfilled</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">orders</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cIf that is the case,<n id=\"1\" /> then <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> is <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st> in my <st data-num=\"0241\" class=\"\">ears</st> and the <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">sound</st> of <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">cattle</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"0595\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st>?\u201d ",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cThey were <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st><n id=\"1\" /> from the <st data-num=\"06003\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>; the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"0834 02550 05921\">spared</st> the <st data-num=\"04315\" class=\"\">best</st> of the <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">flocks</st> and <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">cattle</st> <st data-num=\"04616\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. But <st data-num=\"03498\" class=\"\">everything else</st> we <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">slaughtered</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07503\" class=\"\">Wait a minute</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> Let me <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">tell</st> you <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">what</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> me last <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st>.\u201d Saul<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to him, \u201c<st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">Tell</st> me.\u201d",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cIs it <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> true that <st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">when</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> were <st data-num=\"06996\" class=\"\">insignificant</st> in your own <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">eyes</st>, <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> became <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st> of the <st data-num=\"07626\" class=\"\">tribes</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>? The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"04886\" class=\"\">chose</st><n id=\"1\" /> you as <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> you on a <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">campaign</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">saying</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">Go</st> and <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">exterminate</st> those <st data-num=\"02400\" class=\"\">sinful</st> <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>! <st data-num=\"03898\" class=\"\">Fight</st> against them <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> you<n id=\"2\" /> have <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> them.\u2019",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">haven\u2019t</st> you <st data-num=\"08085 06963\">obeyed</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>? Instead you have <st data-num=\"05860\" class=\"\">greedily rushed</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">upon</st> the <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">plunder</st>! You have <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> <st data-num=\"07451\">what is wrong</st> in the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">estimation</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">But</st> I have <st data-num=\"08085 06963\">obeyed</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>! I <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> on the <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">campaign</st><n id=\"2\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> me <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">on</st>. I <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">brought</st> back <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">Agag</st> of the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st> after <st data-num=\"02763\" class=\"\">exterminating</st> the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>. ",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "But the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st> <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">took</st> from the <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">plunder</st> some of the <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">sheep</st> and <st data-num=\"01241\" class=\"\">cattle</st>\u2014the <st data-num=\"07225\" class=\"\">best</st> of <st data-num=\"02764\" class=\"\">what was to be slaughtered</st>\u2014to <st data-num=\"02076\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st> to the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> in <st data-num=\"01537\" class=\"\">Gilgal</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cDoes the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"02656\" class=\"\">take pleasure</st> in <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st> and <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifices</st><p class=\"poetry\">as much as he does in <st data-num=\"08085 06963 03068\">obedience</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Certainly</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">obedience</st><n id=\"3\" /> is <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">better</st> than <st data-num=\"02077\" class=\"\">sacrifice</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07181\" class=\"\">paying attention</st> is better than<n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"02459\" class=\"\">fat</st> of <st data-num=\"0352\" class=\"\">rams</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"04805\" class=\"\">rebellion</st> is like the <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin</st> of <st data-num=\"07081\" class=\"\">divination</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06484\" class=\"\">presumption</st> is like the <st data-num=\"0205\" class=\"\">evil</st> of <st data-num=\"08655\" class=\"\">idolatry</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03282\" class=\"\">Because</st> you have <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">orders</st>,<n id=\"1\" /><p class=\"poetry\">he has <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> you from being <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"0559\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> I have <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">disobeyed</st> what the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"06310\" class=\"\">commanded</st><n id=\"1\" /> and your <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">words</st> as well. <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I <st data-num=\"03372\">was afraid of</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">army</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> and I <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">obeyed</st> their <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">voice</st>.",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">Now</st> <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">please</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">forgive</st> my <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sin</st>. <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">Go back</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> me so I can <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worship</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.\u201d</p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, \u201cI will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">go back</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> you, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> you have <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">orders</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"03988\" class=\"\">rejected</st> you from <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">being</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"05437\" class=\"\">turned</st> to <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">leave</st>, Saul<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">grabbed</st> the <st data-num=\"03671\" class=\"\">edge</st> of his <st data-num=\"04598\" class=\"\">robe</st> and it <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">tore</st>. ",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him, \u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"07167\" class=\"\">torn</st> the <st data-num=\"04468\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">from</st> you this <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> and has <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> it to one of your <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">colleagues</st> who is <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">better</st> <st data-num=\"04480\" class=\"\">than</st> you!",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"05331\" class=\"\">Preeminent One</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> does <st data-num=\"01571 03808\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08266\" class=\"\">go back on</st> his <st data-num=\"08266\" class=\"\">word</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">change</st> his <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">mind</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">he</st> is <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> a <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">human being</st> who <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">changes</st> his <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">mind</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "Saul<n id=\"1\" /> again <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cI have <st data-num=\"02398\" class=\"\">sinned</st>. <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">please</st> <st data-num=\"03513\" class=\"\">honor</st> me <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> the <st data-num=\"02205\" class=\"\">elders</st> of my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> and <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">Go back</st> <st data-num=\"05973\" class=\"\">with</st> me so I may <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worship</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>.\u201d ",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "So <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">followed</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">back</st>, and <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">worshiped</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"05066 0413\">Bring</st> me <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">Agag</st> of the <st data-num=\"06002\" class=\"\">Amalekites</st>.\u201d So <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">Agag</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> him <st data-num=\"04571\" class=\"\">trembling</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">thinking</st> <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">to himself</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"0403\" class=\"\">Surely</st> <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">death</st> <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"04751\" class=\"\">bitter</st>!\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201cJust <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> your <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">sword</st> <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">left</st> <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st> <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">childless</st>, <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">so</st> your <st data-num=\"0517\" class=\"\">mother</st> will <st data-num=\"07971\">be</st> the most <st data-num=\"07921\" class=\"\">bereaved</st><n id=\"1\" /> among <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">women</st>.\u201d Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"08158\" class=\"\">hacked</st> <st data-num=\"090\" class=\"\">Agag</st> <st data-num=\"08158\" class=\"\">to pieces</st> there in <st data-num=\"01537\" class=\"\">Gilgal</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> to <st data-num=\"07414\" class=\"\">Ramah</st>, while <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">went up</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> his <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">home</st> in <st data-num=\"01390\" class=\"\">Gibeah</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>. ",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "1 Samuel",
    "chapter": "15",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">Until</st> the <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> he<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"04194\" class=\"\">died</st>, <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> did <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03254 07200\">see</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">again</st>. <st data-num=\"08050\" class=\"\">Samuel</st> did, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">however</st>, <st data-num=\"056\" class=\"\">mourn</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, but the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">regretted</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> he had <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">made</st> <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st> <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">over</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "35"
  }
]